  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The second 3x3 Eyes game for the Super Famicom. This time as a side scrolling adventure game with fighting sequences instead of a JRPG.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Lingling discovers a letter left by Fujii, where he reports about a strange tribe that can control beasts. Yakumo is ordered to travel to Nepal, but first he has to find more information about the mysterious tribe by contacting people in Hong-Kong.",
